ParameterItem.Doc: Summation tree type. (Supported trees: Wallace, Array, ZM) (Soon:OS1Tree, OS2Tree) !IMPLEMENTATION!

ParameterItem.Doc: !implementation! AdderType: Indicate the topology to use for the Propogate Generate tree. Ripple type indicates that a ripple chain should be used rather than a tree. ParameterItem.Name: AdderType

ParameterItem.Doc: !placement! Affects the direction that data travels. NW_to_SE indicates will travel from the northwest down to the southeast. Legal Values: NW_to_SE !PHYSICAL!
ParameterItem.Name: Direction
